Leave your comments below.

115
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:33,120
Thanks for watching this episode of China
Uncensored.

116
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,420
Once again I’m Chris Chappell.

117
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,670
See you next time!

